description: Demolition and redevelopment of the site to provide a part 5-, 4- (at southern end only) and 3- storey mixed use development comprising 93 residential flats; new replacement Class B1 office space (1406sq.m) including one commercial unit for flexible B1/A1 business use; 51 car parking spaces; cycle spaces, hard and soft landscaping and revised access (and subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 23/07/2012 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended) and (parking permit-free)
